TextEng: You act as guard. Watch my back.
Hold this spot, and don't move.
I'm dying... This is not good.
Well, have a look at this here.
Everyone group here. Rally around me.
Text: 다들 이리 모여. 내 주위로 집결해.

TextEng: This lock needs to be dealt with carefully.
Scour this area. It should be closely examined.
Text: 이 구역을 샅샅이 뒤져. 자세히 살펴봐야 해.

TextEng: Ugh... This is too much to carry.
I need to get moving. This is a waste of time.
Not bad, not bad at all!
That's a good thought. Good idea.
Bad idea. Not good at all.
You just be careful. I'm warning you...
Back me up here. I need a hand!
That's it! This fight is lost!
Hold this spot. Don't leave it.
I'm hurt bad... Close to dying.

Text: 으... 몸이 안 좋아... 독에 당했어.

TextEng: Not even a dent! This weapon is useless!
This lock should be picked before I put my foot through it.
This place needs a thorough search.
Whoa... This pack is too heavy.
This is boring. I have to find some action.
Rrrazza my... son of a... rrghr!
Quiet now. I've something to say.
That idea, that's a good one.
That idea is just plain bad.
Unless you want to end this in a pool of your own blood, back off!
Text: 네 피 웅덩이에서 끝나고 싶지 않으면 물러서!

TextEng: This battle will be your last!
I require healing. Tend to me.
I need someone by my side. Help me.
I have seen the enemy. Over here.
This battle is lost! Time to retreat!
Watch over me well. Let nothing harm me.
Text: 날 잘 지켜라. 아무것도 해치지 못하게.

TextEng: Hold this spot. Do not move, whatever comes.
Text: 여기를 지켜라. 무슨 일이 있어도 움직이지 마.

TextEng: I'll not last much longer. I'm dying.
My weapon has had no effect?
Rally together around where I stand.
Could you move a moment, please.
This lock needs to be carefully nullified.
I would search this place carefully. There may be something here.
Text: 이곳을 주의 깊게 뒤져야겠어. 뭔가 있을지도 몰라.

TextEng: I carry too much. It will hamper my performance.
Text: 너무 많이 들고 있어. 움직임에 방해가 돼.

TextEng: We should rest if our skills are to be at their best.
We waste too much time. There is much to do.
Text: 시간을 너무 낭비하고 있어. 할 일이 많아.

TextEng: I appreaciate what you have done.
I have something that must be said.
I think that's a fine idea.
I don't think this idea is wise.
Do not temp my anger! You would regret it!
Text: 날 화나게 하지 마! 후회할 거야!

TextEng: Get on them! Attack, attack, attack!
Give it up! You ain't got a chance!
Heal me up! Get to it!
Get on over here! I need a hand!
Time to get the hell out! This one's lost!
Keep an eye on my back. Guard it good.
Just stay right here. Hold this spot.
My spell got messed up. Dammit!
Come on, follow me. Keep up.
Take a look. There's something here.
Gotta get this lock off before I "pick" it with my boot!
Gotta take a good look around here. Might be something...
This is too much. I can't carry all this garbage.
Text: 너무 많아. 이 짐 다 못 들어.

TextEng: I'm tired of this. I need rest now.
Let's get moving. Find some action somewhere!
Listen here. I got something to say.
That's not gonna work. Just a bad idea.
You keep it up and I'll tear you a new hell.
You are SO gonna feel some wrath!
Bring your healing arts unto me. Nowzah!
I need help here. Stand with me.
I see our quarry. There's enemies here.
The fight will be won another day! For now, time to fly!
Bring it to me! I'll give it right back!
Watch my back. Guard it well.
Let no one take this spot. Hold here.
Text: 아무도 이 자리를 빼앗지 못하게. 여기를 지켜.

TextEng: I am injured... This is no way to go out...
I got some bad blood in me... Poisoned...
Step behind me. Follow, my friend.
I have seen something. Look here.
Gather around me. Yes, rally here.
Text: 내 주위로 모여. 그래 여기 집결해.

TextEng: Stand a side a moment. Make way.
A crafty thing, but this lock will be picked.
Text: 교묘하지만 이 자물쇠는 열 수 있어.

TextEng: Look carefully here. I'm sure there's something.
Text: 여기 잘 봐. 분명 뭔가 있어.

TextEng: It is done, done and done.
I can't carry all of this by myself. It's too much.
Text: 혼자 다 못 들어. 너무 많아.

TextEng: Time to lay down my head. I really need to rest.
Text: 머리 좀 눕혀야겠어. 정말 쉬어야 해.

TextEng: There's got to be something better to do than just waiting here.
Text: 여기서 기다리는 것보다 나은 일이 있을 거야.

TextEng: You need to hear the message I bring. You need to!
A right good idea. Yes indeed!
That's just a bad idea. It ain't right.
Keep it up and I'll knock you into LAST week so you can spend until now looking forward to me kicking your tail again!
Text: 계속하면 지난주로 날려버릴 테니까 그때부터 오늘까지 또 맞을 걸 기대하고 있어!

TextEng: I need healing. Tend to my wounds.
I need help here! Aid me!
I have sight of our enemy.
It is time to flee this place!
Attack me then! Let us decide this here!
I am... In need of a healer... Quickly...
Ugh! The energy of my spell has failed.
Walk in my step. Follow me.
There is something here... Out of place.
Text: 여기 뭔가 있어... 어울리지 않는 게.

TextEng: Rally where I stand. Gather here!
Could you move aside? I need a bit of room.
A careful erosion of the lock is needed.
The area should be examined for any... oddities.
Text: 이 지역에 이상한 게 있는지 살펴봐야 해.

TextEng: Let the shadows conceal you, and quickly.
This is beyond me. I can't do this.
Text: 이건 내 능력 밖이야. 못 해.

TextEng: My pack is too heavy. It is difficult to carry.
I think some well-deserved rest is in order.
I'll put down roots if we sit here too long.
Text: 여기 너무 오래 앉아 있으면 뿌리 내리겠어.

TextEng: That's not a very good idea.
Do not pressure me further! I will do as I must!
Text: 더 압박하지 마! 해야 할 일을 할 거야!

TextEng: Quickly, my wounds need tending. Heal me.
I require help here! To my side!
I have seen our enemy. Here.
We must defend this cause another day. Retreat!
Text: 이 대의는 다음에 지켜야 해. 후퇴!

TextEng: Watch over me. Guard me well.
Hold here. Do not retreat from this spot.
Text: 여기 지켜. 이 자리에서 물러나지 마.

TextEng: I can feel it... I'm poisoned.
Walk in my step. Follow me.
Have a look here. Something interesting...
Could you move aside for one moment?
This lock needs to be picked with care.
A search of this place could turn up something.
To the shadows with you! Hide!
I fear I cannot do this.
My pack is too heavy. It is awkward.
My skills should be put to use. Sitting idle is a waste.
Text: 내 기술을 써야 해. 가만히 있는 건 낭비야.

TextEng: I have something that needs saying.
A poor idea. I don't recommend it.
Watch yourself! I will not hesitate to challenge you!
To the fight! Give no quarter!
There is nothing for you here!
I need a healer most immediately. Come here...
Reinforcements to me! Lend me your aid!
I see them. There are enemies here.
Watch over me, please. Guard well.
Hold this place. Do not move from here.
A foul poison... I feel it.
Fall in step as you should. Follow.
Here is something worth a second look.
Text: 여기 다시 볼 만한 게 있어.

TextEng: Gather here. Rally at my location.
If you would, please move to the side.
This lock should be picked with care.
I will see that it is done.
The task is done and taken care of.
I shouldn't be carrying this much.
What is it that YOU want?
I require rest. I am not at my best.
There is no such thing as "fashionably idle." Get moving.
Text: 빈둥거리는 게 멋진 게 아니야. 움직여.

TextEng: Here, come listen to what I have to say.
Text: 이리 와서 내 말 좀 들어봐.

TextEng: A fine idea, I would think.
I doubt that this idea will prove fruitful.
I assure you, I will act with deadly interest if you persist.
Text: 장담하는데 계속하면 목숨 걸고 대응할 거야.

TextEng: I am wounded... Heal me here.
I am in trouble here! Help me if you can!
The enemy of the moment is in my sight.
It is time to concede! We are lost!
Here! Guide your attention to me!
Hold this place. Let nothing uproot you.
Text: 이곳을 지켜. 아무것도 널 뿌리뽑지 못하게.

TextEng: There is a taint... I am poisoned.
By the very earth! I have had... no effect.

Text: 내 주위로 대열을 갖춰. 여기 집결.

TextEng: Give us a little more space, will you?
This lock is perhaps better picked than battered.
Text: 이 자물쇠는 부수는 것보다 따는 게 나을 거야.

TextEng: To the underbrush, hide as best you can.
I cannot do as was asked.
It is done, as it should be.
I carry too much. Walking is difficult...
Day and night are a cycle in balance. I need rest as well.
Text: 낮과 밤은 균형의 순환이야. 나도 쉬어야 해.

TextEng: We add unnecessary length to our journey just lounging about.
I have something that should be heard.
I think that is a fine idea.
Press your actions and I will respond with all the fury of nature!
Text: 계속하면 자연의 모든 분노로 대응할 거야!

TextEng: You have to fight! Come on!
I didn't want to do this but�
Oh, I think I'm hurt� can I get some Healing?
Text: 아 다친 것 같아... 치료 좀 받을 수 있을까?

TextEng: I need some help with this!
I... I see our enemy. Over here.
Run! We have to get away!
You... You come fight me! Right here!
Protect me!  Guard me real good, okay?
I'm sick... I think it's poison...
Aww... My spell got messed up.
Somebody has to take a crack at this lock.
Text: 누가 이 자물쇠 좀 따봐야 해.

TextEng: Oh boy, get hidden real fast!
Sure, I'll see what I can do.
This is way too much. I can't take all this.
Text: 이건 너무 많아. 다 못 들어.

TextEng: Hello there. Can I do something for you?
I sure could use some sleep. Really tired.
May as well be sitting back home for all we do here.
Text: 여기서 이러느니 집에 가서 앉아 있는 게 낫겠어.

TextEng: Um, I've something to say here.
Uh, I don't think that's a good idea.
I� I won't take much more of you� Don't make me hurt you.
Text: 나... 더 이상 못 참아... 나한테 맞고 싶지 않으면 그만해.

TextEng: I need healing! Do it! Now!
Help me here! Back me up!
I seeeee them. The enemy is heeeere.
Come on, fight me here! Come on!
Guard me. Don't let anything get near.
Text: 날 지켜. 아무것도 가까이 못 오게 해.

TextEng: Hold it right here. Don't move from this spot.
Text: 바로 여기 지켜. 이 자리에서 움직이지 마.

TextEng: My spell! For the love of.....
Move aside. Come on, let's go!
This lock should be picked, and quick.
Look carefully here. Search nice and slow.
Text: 여기 주의 깊게 봐. 천천히 뒤져.

TextEng: I can do that. I can.
Text: 할 수 있어. 할 수 있다고.

TextEng: I can't carry this much. It's too heavy.
Text: 이렇게 많이 못 들어. 너무 무거워.

TextEng: I have to get moving... Can't sit still.
No, no, no, that idea's no good.
Text: 아니 아니 아니, 그 생각은 안 돼.

TextEng: You don't want to get me mad, you don't want to get me mad!
Text: 날 화나게 하고 싶지 않을 거야 진짜!

TextEng: To the fight, my friends! Attack!
That's it for you! Take that!
I... I'm in need of a healer's touch... Tend to me.
This could be bad... assist me here!
Shh, we've got company over here.
This fight is lost! Time to go!
This way then! Here! Come on!
Stand your ground on this spot!
I'm not going to last much longer...
I feel it... Yeah, I'm poisoned.
I can't even make a scratch!
Well, have a look at this...
To my side, my fellows! Rally here!
Out of the way. Come on, make room.
This lock requires a delicate touch.
Take a good look around. I bet there's something here.
Text: 주변을 잘 살펴봐. 분명 뭔가 있을 거야.

TextEng: Nope, I just can't get this done.
Whoa, someone take some of this load, will you?
Text: 워, 누가 이 짐 좀 나눠 들어줄래?

TextEng: I should have to say no.
Time for some well earned rest, I think.
Text: 푹 쉴 때가 된 것 같아.

TextEng: Will we chatter the day away? Fortunes are calling!
Text: 하루 종일 수다만 떨 거야? 행운이 부르고 있어!

TextEng: Listen up. I've gotta say something here.
Well, that's just not gonna work. Bad idea.
Text: 그건 안 될 거야. 나쁜 생각이야.

TextEng: If you think you've got the chops to take me, you just keep pushing!
Text: 날 이길 실력이 된다고 생각하면 계속 밀어붙여봐!

TextEng: I could use some healing here!
Give me a hand over here!
Time to go. This one's lost!
I'm dying here. They got me with poison.
Damned magic! My spell is wasted.
Oh boy. My attack is doing nothing over here.
Text: 이런. 내 공격이 전혀 안 먹혀.

TextEng: I'm no packhorse. I can't carry all of this.
Text: 난 짐꾼이 아니야. 다 못 들어.

TextEng: Well, would you look at that!
Psst. Hey, we need to talk.
You keep it up and I'll have to bust your chops.
Text: 계속하면 한 대 맞을 줄 알아.

TextEng: You are nothing to me. Walk away.
You should come here. We must speak.
Beware of what you do, or it might get your skull crushed!
Text: 조심해, 안 그러면 두개골이 박살날 수도 있어!

TextEng: Die and be done with it!
I would have words with you
I swear, I'll wring your neck if you cross me.
Text: 맹세하는데, 날 거스르면 목을 비틀어버릴 거야.

TextEng: Spare a coin for a bit of information?
You just back away. I'll fight if I have to.
I am hurt! Someone heal me!
I have much news! Speak with me!
Taunt me not! I won't allow it!
I'll plant a blade in your gut!
Hey! I've got something to say to you.
You'll soon be hanging from your tongue!
I want to talk to you
I'll have a dagger in your throat if you keep this up.
I ask you. Heal me, please.
Aid me here. I must have help.
You should listen well to what I have to say.
You risk such righteous fury! Change your ways!
Hey come here. I gotta say something.
Text: 야 이리 와. 할 말이 있어.

TextEng: You just leave me alone or... Or... I dunno!
Text: 그냥 날 내버려둬 아니면... 아니면... 모르겠어!

TextEng: Please talk to me. Over here.
Somebody help me! I need help!
Hey, come here. You gotta hear this.
You just watch it! Watch it!
I shall return you to dust!
Blessed be, I am in need of healing.
Help me here. I need assistance
Listen to my words. You must hear them.
Text: 내 말을 들어. 꼭 들어야 해.

TextEng: You do not want to incur my wrath. You do not!
Text: 내 분노를 사고 싶지 않을 거야. 정말이야!

TextEng: Feel the wrath of the heavens!
I am heavily wounded. Heal me.
Rally to me! Aid me here!
Leave me be. I will not tolerate this.
I'll rid the world of you!
Speak with me, if you can.
Watch your step. I will not be treated in this manner!
I bid you speak with me.
Test me futher and I'll put you in your place.
The earth calls for your death!
There is much that you should know.
Do not incure nature's wrath. You would not survive.
Text: 자연의 분노를 사지 마. 살아남지 못할 거야.

TextEng: Attack at my order! I so command!
You are foolish to challenge me!
I am in need. Heal me!
Come to my aid. Help me here.
Come and listen. I must speak with you.
You are a fool to tempt my wrath! You must realize this!
Text: 내 분노를 건드리다니 어리석군! 깨달아야 해!

TextEng: Help me here! Get to it!
You must listen to me here.
I swear I will cut you! You are asking for it!
Come to my side. Aid me here!
You have my attention for the moment.
You do not know the pain you risk!
You face your death in me!
Aid me here! I need assistance!
Do not provoke my wrath. Heed my warning!
Text: 내 분노를 자극하지 마. 경고를 들어!

TextEng: Death to those that threaten balance!
My time has not come! Heal my wounds!
I would speak to you, if I might.
Be wary how you treat me. You cannot fight all of nature.
Text: 날 어떻게 대하는지 조심해. 자연 전체와 싸울 수는 없어.

TextEng: I be needin' to speak to ye!
Keep it up and I'm fer killin' ye, make no mistake!
I will rip you to shreds!
To my side! I command it!
I have something you must hear.
Beware! You risk your very life!
Healing I need. Tend to me!
Well and good! Well and good!
You beware, or you will die!
Nothing else for it now! Attack!
All right, you've had it now!
Time to get what's coming to you!
I could use some healing here. Soon.
Someone want to give me a hand over here?
I need to have a word with you.
Don't... Don't push your luck with me, all right?
I will answer any threat you bring!
You'll not live another day if you push me further!
Do not test me! I shall fight with all the fury I can muster!
Text: 날 건드리지 마! 온 힘을 다해 싸울 거야!

TextEng: Get away from me! Leave me be!
I'll not let you walk away!
I need some healing here. Soon.
To my side. I need help.
Well if that don't beat all.
I've a word or two for you. Better listen up.
Don't make me have to adjust your attitude. I will.
There are no options left! Attack!
You will find no purchase here!
In defense of Right and Justice!
Please, see to my wounds. I am injured.
Help me here. I need assistance!
I will not hesitate to attack if need be. You have been warned!
Text: 필요하면 주저 없이 공격할 거야. 경고했다!

TextEng: All right then, get them! Attack!
I need help. Heal me. Please.
I need someone to give me a hand here.
Come over here. I need to speak with you.
Don't let this get out of hand. Neither of us want that.
Text: 일을 크게 만들지 마. 둘 다 원하는 게 아니잖아.

TextEng: I am no danger to you! Leave me!
I should like to speak with you.
I've seen your type before and I'm NOT scared of you.
Text: 너 같은 놈 전에도 봤어. 안 무서워.

TextEng: Show them what troublemakers get here! Attack!
Heal me! I am sorely wounded!
You'd best leave me be! Just go!
I ain't done nothing to ye!
You there! You should come and have a word or two with me.
I don't take kindly to that sort of thing. Watch yourself.
Text: 그런 건 좋게 안 봐. 조심해.

TextEng: Tis a long day. I could use a drink.
Text: 긴 하루였어. 한 잔 하고 싶군.

TextEng: Tis a fine time for a pint and a few words.
Text: 맥주 한 잔하며 얘기하기 좋은 때군.

TextEng: Buggar off! It�ll be a blade fer your backside, elsewise!
Text: 꺼져! 안 그러면 엉덩이에 칼을 꽂아줄 거야!

TextEng: You re judged, and found wanting!
I am not well at all. Heal me!
I need help here! Help me!
I be needin' a hand, here!
Ye'd best be watchin' yer step around me, fool.
That's the way it's done and done!
I really need to talk to you.
You're in GREAT peril if you bother me. Just you wait!
Text: 날 귀찮게 하면 큰 위험에 처할 거야. 두고 봐!

TextEng: I will cut you down to size!
You're heading for a good beating, you are!
Text: 한 대 맞고 싶어 안달이구나, 그래!

TextEng: I command you attack! All attack!
